text: <https://youtu.be/MgtGHfdpigU|https://youtu.be/MgtGHfdpigU> cool YouTube channel called ASMR programming. He does a lot of cool little projects. No tutorials, just a video of him programing, and it’s quite relaxing. Thought one of the reasons I posted this is he has hit GitHub link in the description. So some of these that he does could be good little side project ideas!
